{
  "stem": "12666.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was strapped to a table, and they have multiple fracture of her legs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would use different methods to try to cure her, and they, they were very proud.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, oh, we contributed something to medicine because we found out that the steel rod does mend the bones.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they didn't even bother to sew her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when she showed her legs, they were a horrible, you know, mess.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but she was very pretty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was very popular.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But it shows you that they did conduct experiments.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And actually, the Germans lawyers told us, well, you did commit some atrocities, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They says, Marines in the Pacific and Guadalcanal, they used to cut the ears of the Japanese and wearing them on their belt.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the difference is that our atrocities were not planned by our government.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were spontaneous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "People facing horrors of people smeared with honey and being killed by the Japanese, and so on, so that was a reaction, and it was not here.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "All the experiments that the Nazis committed were planned by the government.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that was a difference between the Allies and between-- in fact, when we had training for interrogation of prisoners of war, we thought that the only way to make a, a German confess is to bring the biggest fellow and say that he is a Pole whose family was killed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we would leave you with him, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He has a score to settle, and we will leave the tent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The German would get so scared, he would spill the beans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't use any.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT]",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
